WEBVTT

00:13:00.562 --> 00:13:02.922
Reddit cofounder, Alexis Ohanian,

00:13:02.946 --> 00:13:06.674
demonstrated that not all active
allyship needs to be so serious.

00:13:07.057 --> 00:13:09.933
He stepped up to support
a 15-year-old Muslim girl's mission

00:13:09.957 --> 00:13:12.004
to introduce a hijab emoji.

00:13:12.028 --> 00:13:13.541
(Laughter)

00:13:14.035 --> 00:13:15.624
It's a simple gesture,

00:13:15.648 --> 00:13:18.185
but it has a significant
subconscious impact

00:13:18.209 --> 00:13:21.448
on normalizing and humanizing Muslims,

00:13:21.472 --> 00:13:24.117
including the community
as a part of an "us"

00:13:24.141 --> 00:13:25.825
instead of an "other."

00:13:27.352 --> 00:13:29.669
The editor in chief
of Women's Running magazine

00:13:29.693 --> 00:13:33.780
just put the first hijabi to ever be
on the cover of a US fitness magazine.